<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Maintenance Completed - 12done.com</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #4F46E5; }
    .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #4F46E5; }
    .content { padding: 30px 0; }
    .completed-badge { background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .checkmark-box { text-align: center; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .checkmark { font-size: 48px; color: #10B981; }
    .details-box { background: #ECFDF5; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; }
    .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #D1FAE5; }
    .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .detail-label { color: #047857; font-weight: 500; }
    .detail-value { color: #065F46; }
    .notes-box { background: #F0FDF4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
    .confirm-note { background: #FEF3C7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; color: #666; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">12done.com</div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="completed-badge">Work Completed</div>

    <h1>Maintenance work has been completed!</h1>

    <div class="checkmark-box">
      <div class="checkmark">&#10004;</div>
    </div>

    <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

    <p>The service provider has marked the maintenance work as completed for your request.</p>

    <div class="details-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Completion Details</h3>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Property</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{propertyTitle}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Issue</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{title}}</span>
      </div>
      {{#if actualCost}}
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Final Cost</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{actualCost}} EUR</span>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    {{#if completionNotes}}
    <div class="notes-box">
      <strong>Provider Notes:</strong>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">{{completionNotes}}</p>
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="confirm-note">
      <strong>Action Required:</strong> Please confirm that the work has been completed satisfactorily. Both tenant and landlord need to confirm to close this request.
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Confirm Completion</a>
    </p>

    <p>If you have any concerns about the work performed, please contact your landlord or the service provider through the platform.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The 12done.com Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; {{year}} 12done.com. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This is a transactional email regarding property maintenance on 12done.com.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
